{"word":"λαιψηρός","slug":"λαιψηρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λαιψηρός</b></el> <el>(λαιψηρός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:αἰψηρός'><el>αἰψηρός</el></a>\n<p/><i>light, nimble, swift</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>swiftly</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}